0:55:43.000Z","msg":"同華拉膠一樣咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0e40a94d080145e5dc4a417728cda0b0fa400a","tid":2338110,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T20:56:06.000Z","msg":"重開la<br />\n又252<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ae59ea8bc1b44d363e7a1029b6b7162282ce8b","tid":2338110,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef0e40a94d080145e5dc4a417728cda0b0fa400a","tid":2338110,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T20:56:06.000Z","msg":"重開la<br />\n又252<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T20:56:57.000Z","msg":"唉 樓主超廢"},{"pid":"d2627ff5ac3eed075de044b5951ece6ac7d321d3","tid":2338110,"uid":30967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T20:57:59.000Z","msg":"辛係咪轉左著adidas"},{"pid":"4b972df30ead9e6b3ef69cc3a423523de1a2d8ab","tid":2338110,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2627ff5ac3eed075de044b5951ece6ac7d321d3","tid":2338110,"uid":30967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T20:57:59.000Z","msg":"辛係咪轉左著adidas"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T20:58:28.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"ff1cf8b5180d0f93aba25544798f684f273a1e3c","tid":2338110,"uid":87672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T00:19:54.000Z","msg":"場場都補時先入多粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0c636636e952459008521f6067ea0c1006ffa1","tid":2338110,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T00:55:42.000Z","msg":"施丹再爆粗：太難打唔出夏沙特<br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports】又一次，法國球王施丹又爆粗，這次是源於打敗格拉納達後，覺得吃力。<br />\n皇家馬德里周三在西甲憑卡斯美路、賓斯馬各建一功，主場贏格拉納達2:0，賽後追至與馬德里體育會同得32分並列榜首，但多賽兩場。教練施丹賽後難掩興奮：「這是一場蠱惑的比賽，是一場他媽的（f***ing）硬仗，對手前來壓逼。上半場艱難，下半場好多了。<br />\n<br />\n施丹早前在馬德里打吡贏馬體育會也曾忘形爆粗，大讚一眾成功演繹賽前部署的球員「他媽的無與倫比（f***ing brilliant）」。<br />\n<br />\n「我實在為球員感到高興，因為這類比賽殊非容易。依下半場的表現，我們值得獲勝。」皇馬在西甲5連勝，施丹亦不忘讚賞球員比賽態度及準備工夫充足。夏沙特今仗列作後備，然而最終沒落場，施丹解釋：「我不應為派他出賽是恰當，這是一場硬仗，我不欲讓他冒險。他很好，但需要按部就班。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"7d75912e5dcee24248ff715cd8ccc0be1375ce47","tid":2338110,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T01:43:34.000Z","msg":"過返253"}]}